descriptionNullable: 572 unique images, split into a training folder of 500 images and a validation folder of 72 images. Dataset is split 50:50 between images of turtles and penguins. Each image contains exactly one instance of an object. Accompanying annotation information is a list of dictionaries. Bounding box coordinates are provided in Pascal VOC format. Category IDs include 0 (background), 1 (penguin) and 2 (turtle).
title: Penguins vs Turtles
subtitle: Image classification with bounding boxes
